title: Quang Minh - Mosquito Net Door
description:
- An anti-mosquito screen door that pulls up and down based on a self-winding spring system installed on the door frame
- Open and close the net door easily by dragging and dropping the rope
- Vertical rolling doors have a compact design, bringing convenience and modernity to the house.
- Chosen by many customers
- Doors are usually installed in windows or openings to get wind and natural light
